  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are the ship's cat, responsible for pest control on the world first nuclear powered passenger ship. Move through the ship exploring the passenger and crew areas, gaining new powers as you progress.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595040/extras/638bd2afc8c0f11fd0456b562f997008.poster.avif?t=1765942427\" width=640 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595040/extras/638bd2afc8c0f11fd0456b562f997008.webm?t=1765942427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595040/extras/638bd2afc8c0f11fd0456b562f997008.mp4?t=1765942427\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is an action adventure that is easy to play. It has a linear story as seen from the cat's point of view. There is some humour, a fair bit of mystery, and a small amount of scariness and horror. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595040/extras/e96db4b31aa96600507f293b544721ca.poster.avif?t=1765942427\" width=640 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595040/extras/e96db4b31aa96600507f293b544721ca.webm?t=1765942427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595040/extras/e96db4b31aa96600507f293b544721ca.mp4?t=1765942427\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are the ship's cat, responsible for pest control on the world first nuclear powered passenger ship. Move through the ship exploring the passenger and crew areas, gaining new powers as you progress.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595040/extras/638bd2afc8c0f11fd0456b562f997008.poster.avif?t=1765942427\" width=640 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595040/extras/638bd2afc8c0f11fd0456b562f997008.webm?t=1765942427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595040/extras/638bd2afc8c0f11fd0456b562f997008.mp4?t=1765942427\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is an action adventure that is easy to play. It has a linear story as seen from the cat's point of view. There is some humour, a fair bit of mystery, and a small amount of scariness and horror. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595040/extras/e96db4b31aa96600507f293b544721ca.poster.avif?t=1765942427\" width=640 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595040/extras/e96db4b31aa96600507f293b544721ca.webm?t=1765942427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2595040/extras/e96db4b31aa96600507f293b544721ca.mp4?t=1765942427\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
